    {
      "id": "5a202591_24b0bcf3",
      "file_path": "controlloop/templates/template.demo/pom.xml",
      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 14,
      "message": "We use drools 6.5.   That's the drools version we use.   If have problems finding them, it is probably the maven coordinates not being right.   I saw that in some other places it is using 6.5 for drools artifacts.\n\nFurther, I believe they are only used for testing, so mark them as <scope> test.\n\nWe have to be tidy with dependencies, we don't want to be loading all these unnecessary ones, with the deployment of a control loop.",
